    <item>
      <title>西非军政府获六个月时间重新考虑退出贸易集团</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/west-african-juntas-given-six-months-to-rethink-trade-bloc-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西非领导人给予马里、尼日尔和布基纳法索军事领导人更多时间重新考虑脱离该地区经济集团的决定，作为避免该集团分裂的最后一次努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/west-african-juntas-given-six-months-to-rethink-trade-bloc-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 19:09:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊总理表示将对银行汇款费用设定上限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/greece-to-impose-cap-on-bank-fees-for-money-transfers-pm-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊总理基里亚科斯·米佐塔基斯周日表示，希腊将对银行收取的汇款费用设定上限，同时人们在支付账单时将无需支付任何费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/greece-to-impose-cap-on-bank-fees-for-money-transfers-pm-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 18:34:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普助推的美元涨势明年年底将面临现实考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/dollar-s-trump-fueled-gains-face-a-reality-check-late-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的政策和美联储的降息可能会在 2025 年下半年给美元带来压力，华尔街开始对美元感到失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/dollar-s-trump-fueled-gains-face-a-reality-check-late-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 17:25:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
