    <item>
      <title>如果工作岗位得以保留，意大利 Meloni 愿意与 Stellantis 合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/italy-s-meloni-ready-to-work-with-stellantis-if-jobs-are-kept</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼表示，意大利政府愿意与 Stellantis NV 合作，帮助该汽车制造商开辟新的发展道路，但前提是该公司能在意大利保留就业岗位和工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/italy-s-meloni-ready-to-work-with-stellantis-if-jobs-are-kept</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 14:20:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巨额利息负担困扰 29 万亿美元新兴市场债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/massive-interest-burden-haunts-29-trillion-emerging-debt-pile</link>
      <description><![CDATA[发展中国家已注定要迎来动荡的2025年，而且还要应对过去十年间累积的29万亿美元债务不断膨胀的利息支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/massive-interest-burden-haunts-29-trillion-emerging-debt-pile</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>24 小时降息结束全球央行宽松政策年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/fed-interest-rates-24-hours-of-cuts-that-end-year-of-global-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年是通货膨胀率下降到足以让大多数发达经济体开始放松货币政策的一年，而随着美联储牵头的 24 小时连续决策，这一年即将结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/fed-interest-rates-24-hours-of-cuts-that-end-year-of-global-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
